description: The affected person was identified seven days into self-isolation after returning from the UK.
title: Coronavirus: Guernsey has first case in 130 days
title_page: Coronavirus: Guernsey has first case in 130 days - BBC News
maintext: Dr Brink said: "Whilst I know this announcement will concern members of the community, it is important to remember that we have robust systems in place to identify cases and then track and trace any contacts.
